OL,3,GCentral, Tayside & Fife
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FIt will be a
OL,6,Fmainly dry but rather cloudy evening
OL,7,Fand night, with just the odd spot of
OL,8,Flight rain or drizzle possible in the
OL,9,Fhills.
OL,10,
OL,11,CWednesday:FDry and bright but rather
OL,12,Fcloudy, with the best chance of
OL,13,Fbrighter spells developing during the
OL,14,Fafternoon.
OL,15,
OL,16,COutlook for Thursday to Saturday:FDry
OL,17,Fand warm Thursday with sunny spells,
OL,18,Fbut cloudier, cooler east coast at
OL,19,Ftimes. Variable cloud and bright
OL,20,Fspells Friday, patchy rain possible in
OL,21,Fwest. Dry start Saturday, rain later.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
